758
00:58:14,509 --> 00:58:16,209
Di mana itu?

759
00:58:25,489 --> 00:58:26,489
Apa di dalam sana?

760
00:58:33,330 --> 00:58:34,630
Itu dia.

761
00:58:46,279 --> 00:58:47,350
Apa kamu gila?

762
